<style>
  .shipping-page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--page-padding);
  }

  .shipping-page__title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .shipping-page h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .shipping-page p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .shipping-page ul {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .shipping-page li {
    list-style: disc;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .shipping-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .shipping-table th,
  .shipping-table td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .shipping-table th {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
</style>

<div class="shipping-page">
  <h1 class="heading-1 shipping-page__title">Shipping & Delivery</h1>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Domestic Shipping</h2>
  <p>All Australian orders include free express shipping via Australia Post. No minimum order required.</p>

  <table class="shipping-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Method</th>
        <th>Delivery Time</th>
        <th>Cost</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Express Post</td>
        <td>2-5 business days</td>
        <td>Free</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Standard Post</td>
        <td>5-10 business days</td>
        <td>Free</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Order Tracking</h2>
  <p>Full tracking is provided for all orders. Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with your tracking number. Track your order at any time via Australia Post.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">International Shipping</h2>
  <p>International shipping is available at checkout. Rates and delivery times vary by destination. International orders may be subject to import duties and taxes, which are the responsibility of the recipient.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Processing Time</h2>
  <p>Orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed on the next business day.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Packaging</h2>
  <p>Every piece arrives in our signature jewelry box with a Certificate of Authenticity and microfiber polishing cloth. Gift-ready, no additional wrapping needed.</p>

  <h2 class="heading-3">Questions?</h2>
  <p>Contact our team at <a href="mailto:hello@theclearcut.com.au" style="text-decoration:underline;">hello@theclearcut.com.au</a> for any shipping enquiries.</p>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping Page",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
